            <title>[CASSANDRA-16608] Nodetool verify fixes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16608</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A few issues with nodetool verify:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Include cause exception when it fails verifying an sstable&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Don&apos;t try to check if the node owns tokens from localpartitioner sstables&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Don&apos;t try to deserialise non-existing bloom filter file&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
